sentence.text: Pre-NACT core needle biopsies and postoperative tumor samples were immunohistochemically stained for nuclear factor erythroid 2-related factor 2 (positive regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II), Kelch-like ECH-associated protein 1 (proteasomal ubiquitin-independent protein catabolic process), thioredoxin (Trx), and peroxiredoxin I (Prx I).

entity.text: positive regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II
